text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_VitoIntro {
	"I trained together with my whole family,
	every one of us!
	I'm not losing to anyone!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_VitoDefeat {
	"Better than my family?!
	Is that possible?!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_VitoPostBattle {
	"I was better than everyone in my
	family. I've never lost before…

	I've lost my confidence…
	Maybe I'll go home…"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_OwenIntro {
	"I'd heard that there was a tough
	little kid around. Do they mean you?"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_OwenDefeat {
	"The little shrimp is tough!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_OwenPostBattle {
	"The rumors I heard, that tough little
	kid is from PETALBURG CITY."
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_CarolineIntro {
	"You must be getting a little tired."
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_CarolineDefeat {
	"No signs of tiring at all!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_CarolinePostBattle {
	"VICTORY ROAD and the POKéMON LEAGUE
	are long and grueling challenges.
	Beware of fatigue!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_JulieIntro {
	"You shouldn't get complacent just
	because you have a lot of GYM BADGES.

	There's always going to be someone
	who's better than you!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_JulieDefeat {
	"You're better than me!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_JuliePostBattle {
	"Gaze on your collected BADGES and
	remember the TRAINERS you've faced."
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_FelixIntro {
	"I've come this far, but the tension's
	giving me awful stomach pain…"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_FelixDefeat {
	"Ooh…
	It hurts…"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_FelixPostBattle {
	"I can't help getting all tense knowing
	that I'm nearing the POKéMON LEAGUE.

	It's all I can do to feign calm."
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_DianneIntro {
	"The elite among the elite gather in
	this cave.

	How are you finding it?"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_DianneDefeat {
	"Not rattled in the least bit!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B2F_Text_DiannePostBattle {
	"You do have guts! I like that!
	Keep it going!"
}
